<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{ doc.numero }} · Manifiesto de Carga</title>
<style>
  {{ fontStyle | raw }}
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; }
  :root { --ink: #0f0f10; --ink-2: #4a4a50; --ink-3: #8c8c94; --accent: #ff5a1f; --accent-soft: #fff1ea; --line: #e8e6df; --paper: #fbfaf4; }
  body { font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink); background: var(--paper); width: 1123px; min-height: 794px; padding: 28px 36px; }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  p { margin: 0; }

  .top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 16px; align-items: stretch; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .id-left { padding: 14px 16px; border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); border-radius: 4px; background: #fff; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .id-left .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 9px; }
  .id-left .logo { width: 36px; height: 36px; flex: none; background: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .id-left .logo svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
  .id-left .logo img { max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
  .id-left .co-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.05; }
  .id-left .co-tag { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 1px; font-weight: 500; }
  .id-left .info { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); display: grid; gap: 1px; }
  .id-left .info b { color: var(--ink); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

  .id-right { padding: 13px 16px; background: var(--ink); color: #fff; border-radius: 4px; }
  .id-right .kind { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.03em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .id-right .subkind { font-size: 8.5px; opacity: 0.62; margin-top: 1px; }
  .id-right .num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin: 6px 0 8px; letter-spacing: 0.01em; }
  .id-right .rule { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16); margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .id-right .f { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .id-right .f .k { font-size: 9px; opacity: 0.6; white-space: nowrap; }
  .id-right .f .v { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 600; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

  .sec-label { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .sec-label .t { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .sec-label .c { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-3); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  .items-wrap { background: #fff; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden; }
  .items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; }
  .items thead th { font-size: 8.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; text-align: left; padding: 9px 10px; background: var(--ink); }
  .items tbody td { padding: 8px 10px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .items tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #faf9f3; }
  .items .c-fecha { width: 70px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-serie { width: 96px; }
  .items .c-taquito { width: 104px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-placa { width: 70px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .c-bul, .items .c-weight, .items .c-flete { text-align: right; }
  .items .c-bul { width: 52px; font-weight: 700; }
  .items .c-weight { width: 78px; color: var(--ink-2); font-weight: 600; }
  .items .c-flete { width: 84px; font-weight: 700; }
  .items .c-pago { width: 104px; }
  .items .party { font-weight: 600; word-break: break-word; }
  .items .pago { padding-right: 8px; }
  .items .pago .pill { display: inline-block; font-size: 8px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.02em; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 999px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .items .pago .pill.cancelado { background: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); }
  .items .pago .pill.cobrar { background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent); }
  .items .pago .pill.pce { border: 1px solid var(--line); color: var(--ink-2); }
  .items tfoot td { padding: 9px 10px; background: var(--accent-soft); border-top: 2px solid var(--ink); font-weight: 800; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .items tfoot .lbl { text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .items tfoot .c-bul, .items tfoot .c-weight, .items tfoot .c-flete { text-align: right; }
  .items tfoot .c-flete { padding-left: 6px; }

  .foot { margin-top: 18px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .foot .note { font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .foot .note strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .foot .note .badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 8.5px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; white-space: nowrap; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top">
  <div class="id-left">
    <div class="mark">
      <div class="logo">{% if params.logo is not empty %}<img src="{{ params.logo }}" alt="logo"/>{% else %}<svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="14"/><path d="M9 23l5-9 6 4 6-7"/></svg>{% endif %}</div>
      <div>
        <div class="co-name">{{ doc.emisorRazonSocial }}</div>
        {% if doc.emisorNombreComercial is not empty and doc.emisorNombreComercial != doc.emisorRazonSocial %}<div class="co-tag">{{ doc.emisorNombreComercial }}</div>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
      {% if doc.emisorDireccion is not empty %}<span>{{ doc.emisorDireccion }}</span>{% endif %}
      {% if doc.emisorUbicacion is not empty %}<span>{{ doc.emisorUbicacion }}</span>{% endif %}
      {% if doc.emisorEmail is not empty or doc.emisorTelefono is not empty %}<span>{% if doc.emisorEmail is not empty %}{{ doc.emisorEmail }}{% endif %}{% if doc.emisorEmail is not empty and doc.emisorTelefono is not empty %} · {% endif %}{{ doc.emisorTelefono }}</span>{% endif %}
      <span>RUC <b>{{ doc.emisorRuc }}</b>{% if doc.emisorRegistroMtc is not empty %} · Reg. MTC <b>{{ doc.emisorRegistroMtc }}</b>{% endif %}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="id-right">
    <div class="kind">Manifiesto de Carga</div>
    <div class="subkind">Documento interno de control</div>
    <div class="num">{{ doc.numero }}</div>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <div class="f"><span class="k">Fecha de salida</span><span class="v">{% if doc.fechaSalida is not null %}{{ doc.fechaSalida|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</span></div>
    {% if doc.serie is not empty %}<div class="f"><span class="k">Serie · N°</span><span class="v">{{ doc.serie }} · {{ doc.numero }}</span></div>{% endif %}
    <div class="f"><span class="k">Guías · bultos</span><span class="v">{{ doc.totalGuias }} · {{ doc.totalBultos }}</span></div>
    <div class="f"><span class="k">Peso · flete</span><span class="v">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }} kg · S/ {{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="sec-label">
  <span class="t">Carga consolidada — guías de remisión</span>
  <span class="c">{{ doc.totalGuias }} guías</span>
</div>
<div class="items-wrap">
<table class="items">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th class="c-fecha">F. Emisión</th>
      <th class="c-serie">Serie · N°</th>
      <th class="c-taquito">N° Tracking</th>
      <th>Remitente</th>
      <th>Destino</th>
      <th class="c-placa">Placa</th>
      <th class="c-weight">Peso kg</th>
      <th class="c-bul">Bultos</th>
      <th class="c-flete">Flete S/</th>
      <th class="c-pago">Pago</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for l in doc.lineas %}
    <tr>
      <td class="c-fecha mono">{% if l.fechaEmision is not null %}{{ l.fechaEmision|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</td>
      <td class="c-serie mono">{{ l.guiaSerieNumero }}</td>
      <td class="c-taquito mono">{{ l.taquito }}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.remitente }}</td>
      <td class="party">{{ l.destinoDistrito }}</td>
      <td class="c-placa mono">{{ l.placa }}</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ l.peso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ l.bultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ l.flete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="pago">{% if l.condicionPago is not empty %}<span class="pill {{ l.pagoClase }}">{{ l.condicionPago }}</span>{% endif %}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <td class="lbl" colspan="6">Total · {{ doc.totalGuias }} guías consolidadas</td>
      <td class="c-weight mono">{{ doc.totalPeso|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-bul mono">{{ doc.totalBultos }}</td>
      <td class="c-flete mono">{{ doc.totalFlete|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-pago"></td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
</div>

<div class="foot">
  <div class="note">
    <span class="badge">● Uso interno</span>
    <p>Documento de <strong>control de carga consolidada</strong> para el viaje. No constituye comprobante de pago ni guía de remisión electrónica; cada guía se sustenta de forma individual.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
